Rating: 4
Delicious! I first sauteed chopped onions & garlic in oil & butter until well browned, then added the Brussels sprouts (the bigger of which I cut in half) and sauteed it all with more oil & butter until they were all well browned. I like them all to be nicely sauteed, so I think they're better all cut in half.

